body.name: AODK L Shaped Computer Desk with Power Outlets & 3 Cloth Drawers, Reversible Office Desk with Shelves & Monitor Stand, Corner Desk with USB Ports, Study Desk Writing Table for Bedroom, White, 71 Inch

climatePledgeFriendly.details: The Forest Stewardship Council certified products support responsible forestry, helping keep forests healthy for future generations.

features: 【Reversible Design & Multiple Forms】This table can be 58 inch or 71 inch wide depending on where the drawers are installed. The chest of drawers can be installed under or next to the main desk. The side desk with shelves can be installed to the left or right of the main desk. Variable desk shape allows you to adjust the desk to suit your personal preferences, providing you with a more comfortable and efficient workplace.

【USB Charging Ports & Power Outlets】The PC desk is equipped with 2 power outlets and 2 USB charging ports for your electronic devices. You can easily and conveniently charge your smart phone, gaming gear and Bluetooth devices when you are working or playing games.

【Desk with Drawers & Shelves】This office desk has 3 fabric drawers, a host stand, and a 2-tier shelf. Ample storage space allows items such as books, stationery, files, electronics, ornaments, etc. to be organized and accessible, so you'll have a large, clean desktop that will make you feel good.

【Large Desk & Monitor Stand】The L desk measures 58"/71"(L) x 31.5"(W) x 34.6"(H) with a 47.2"(L) x 7.8"(W) monitor stand, providing a spacious workstation for writing, studying and gaming. Enough for two monitors, the monitor stand elevates your line of sight, allowing you to maintain proper sitting posture and protect your cervical and spinal health.

【Easy Assembly & After-sale Service】The gaming desk comes with detailed instructions, all parts are clearly labeled, what you need to do is following instructions step-by-step. If your AODK desk arrives damaged, missing parts or scratched, please feel free to contact us, our professional customer support team will help you solve the problem within 24 hours.

【Stylish & Practical】A clean and simple look that fits just about anywhere. Modern office desk is suitable for study room, bedroom, living room, game room, children's room, office. The Wood desk can be used as computer desk, a study desk, a gaming computer desk, an office table, a work desk, a home desk, a workstation. The large space and comfortable study table design allow you to complete whatever you want at home.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute, functional desk!
reviews.reviewText: This desk is perfect for small areas. It was pretty easy to assemble, looks great, and feels very sturdy. My only complaint is with the drawers, which are made like those collapsible square organizers. Same material and construction, with a faux leather front. They feel pretty flimsy and don't slide in and out very smoothly. I don't feel like they'd hold much weight without taking damage. But it's a pretty minor thing, not even worth taking a star off for. All in all, great desk at a great price!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Not a desk for ants.
reviews.reviewText: This desk is a game-changer! It’s so small that it makes me feel like a giant. I can finally live out my dream of being a giant without having to go through the hassle of growing to 50 feet tall. The desk is so small that it’s perfect for people who want to work from home but don’t want to feel like they’re actually working. The power outlets and USB charging port are a great addition, but I’m still waiting for the day when they invent a desk that can charge my phone while I lay in bed. Overall, I’d say this desk is perfect for anyone who wants to feel like a giant while they work.
